onnxruntime>=1.16
# NOTE on the transformers/optimum chain (2026-05-07):
#   - transformers 5.x removed `is_tf_available` from `transformers.utils`,
#     which optimum 1.17.1 still imports.
#   - The published HuggingFace ONNX PII model also has a tokenizer/model
#     mismatch (tokenizer emits `token_type_ids`, model has no such input).
#     This makes neural redaction non-functional regardless of versions.
#   Net effect: neural PII detection has been off in prod since the model
#   shipped. Pattern recognizers (credit card / IBAN / email regex) still
#   run and cover financial PII. We keep `transformers>=5.8.0` so the
#   import error path triggers cleanly — the engine caches the exception,
#   the redactor logs it once per process, and behavior degrades to
#   pattern-only without spam. Re-evaluate the whole chain when a
#   compatible model + optimum + transformers tuple is established.
transformers>=5.8.0
optimum[onnxruntime]>=1.14
